{"type":"message","id":"b6fbf2d0","parentId":"fd408a16","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:28:59.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about what skills I currently have available. I can see from my system prompt that there's a list of available skills. Let me summarize them for him.\n\nLooking at the skills list from the system prompt, I have quite a few. Let me organize them in a readable way.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n目前装了 71 个技能，按功能大致分几类：\n\n**写作/文档**\n- docx、pptx、xlsx、pdf、docx-coauthoring\n\n**前端/设计**\n- frontend-design、canvas-design、algorithmic-art、web-artifacts-builder、theme-factory\n\n**网页/数据抓取**\n- web-scout、web-scraping、playwright-scraper-skill、multi-search-engine\n\n**开发相关**\n- coding-agent、mcp-builder、mcp-integration、debug、verify/verification-agent\n\n**通讯/社交**\n- slack-gif-creator、create-colleague\n\n**效率/管理**\n- taskflow、taskflow-inbox-triage、healthcheck、proactive-agent、remember、session-logs、context-compact\n\n**其他**\n- weather、video-frames、keybindings、htm、simplify、skill-creator、skill-packaging、agent-lifecycle-mgr、behavior-design、blast-radius-permission、brand-guidelines、claude-api、claudeInChrome、douyin-downloader、douyin-video-analyst、ecommerce-competitor-analysis、find-skills-skill、internal-comms、loop、node-connect、prompt-engineering-expert、self-improving-agent、stuck、tmux、updateConfig、webapp-testing\n\n需要哪个的具体用法，直接说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777048126124,"responseId":"chatcmpl-j0v092ossndnj2ygjci45"}}
