{"type":"message","id":"ad809bb0","parentId":"f1b2788f","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:29:43.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问网页抓取数据用的什么技能，我需要列出相关的抓取类技能并说明各自用途。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n网页抓取主要靠这几个技能：\n\n**轻量级（直接抓取页面内容）**\n- **web-scout** — 通用网页内容抓取，适合快速获取页面信息\n- **web-scraping** — 更侧重结构化数据提取\n\n**浏览器自动化（需要渲染的页面）**\n- **playwright-scraper-skill** — 基于 Playwright，能处理 JS 渲染、登录、交互等复杂场景\n\n**搜索辅助**\n- **multi-search-engine** — 多搜索引擎搜索，配合抓取用\n\n日常用 `web-scout` 或 `web-scraping` 就够了，遇到需要登录或 JS 渲染的页面就切 `playwright`。需要我演示哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777048175356,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a1wb4dr7hc8xmqjiy3ljhq"}}
