{"type":"message","id":"59e42f2f","parentId":"d381f385","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:33:25.543Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"188550953","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"opencli — available commands\n\n  1688\n    assets [cookie] — 列出 1688 商品页可提取的图片/视频素材\n    download [cookie] — 批量下载 1688 商品页可提取的图片和视频素材\n    item [cookie] — 1688 商品详情（公开商品字段、价格阶梯、卖家基础信息）\n    search [cookie] — 1688 商品搜索（结果候选、卖家链接、价格/MOQ/销量文本）\n    store [cookie] — 1688 店铺/供应商公开信息（联系方式、主营、入驻年限、公开服务信号）\n\n  36kr\n    article [intercept] — 获取36氪文章正文内容\n    hot [public] — 36氪热榜 — trending articles (renqi/zonghe/shoucang/catalog)\n    news [public] — Latest tech/startup news from 36kr (36氪)\n    search [public] — 搜索36氪文章\n\n  amazon\n    bestsellers [cookie] — Amazon Best Sellers pages for category candidate discovery\n    discussion [cookie] — Amazon review summary and sample customer discussion from product review pages\n    movers-shakers [cookie] — Amazon Movers & Shakers pages for short-term growth signals\n    new-releases [cookie] — Amazon New Releases pages for early momentum discovery\n    offer [cookie] — Amazon seller, buy box, and fulfillment facts from the product page\n    product [cookie] — Amazon product page facts for candidate validation\n    search [cookie] — Amazon search results for product discovery and coarse filtering\n\n  antigravity\n    dump [ui] — Dump the DOM to help AI understand the UI\n    extract-code [ui] — Extract multi-line code blocks from the current Antigravity conversation\n    model [ui] — Switch the active LLM model in Antigravity\n    new [ui] — Start a new conversation / clear context in Antigravity"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7126,"aggregated":"opencli — available commands\n\n  1688\n    assets [cookie] — 列出 1688 商品页可提取的图片/视频素材\n    download [cookie] — 批量下载 1688 商品页可提取的图片和视频素材\n    item [cookie] — 1688 商品详情（公开商品字段、价格阶梯、卖家基础信息）\n    search [cookie] — 1688 商品搜索（结果候选、卖家链接、价格/MOQ/销量文本）\n    store [cookie] — 1688 店铺/供应商公开信息（联系方式、主营、入驻年限、公开服务信号）\n\n  36kr\n    article [intercept] — 获取36氪文章正文内容\n    hot [public] — 36氪热榜 — trending articles (renqi/zonghe/shoucang/catalog)\n    news [public] — Latest tech/startup news from 36kr (36氪)\n    search [public] — 搜索36氪文章\n\n  amazon\n    bestsellers [cookie] — Amazon Best Sellers pages for category candidate discovery\n    discussion [cookie] — Amazon review summary and sample customer discussion from product review pages\n    movers-shakers [cookie] — Amazon Movers & Shakers pages for short-term growth signals\n    new-releases [cookie] — Amazon New Releases pages for early momentum discovery\n    offer [cookie] — Amazon seller, buy box, and fulfillment facts from the product page\n    product [cookie] — Amazon product page facts for candidate validation\n    search [cookie] — Amazon search results for product discovery and coarse filtering\n\n  antigravity\n    dump [ui] — Dump the DOM to help AI understand the UI\n    extract-code [ui] — Extract multi-line code blocks from the current Antigravity conversation\n    model [ui] — Switch the active LLM model in Antigravity\n    new [ui] — Start a new conversation / clear context in Antigravity","cwd":"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777048405533}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f721c57","parentId":"59e42f2f","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:33:35.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenCLI is installed locally at `/home/kensoulstar/OpenCLI-main` but not globally. The user wants to use it as a skill in OpenClaw. Let me check how to integrate it.\n\nThe user is asking if they can use OpenCLI's capabilities. The answer is: yes, but it needs to be integrated. Let me check if there's a skill directory in OpenClaw for this.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOpenCLI 确实装了，但只在本地项目目录里，没装成全局命令。功能很强大——90+ 站点的 CLI 接口，B站热榜、小红书、知乎、Amazon、Twitter/X 都能直接调。\n\n要让它能在 OpenClaw 里用，有两个方向：\n\n1. **全局安装** — `npm install -g @jackwener/opencli`，然后我直接 `exec` 调用\n2. **注册为 OpenClaw 技能** — 写一个 skill 包装 opencli 命令，这样更规范\n\n你想怎么搞？先全局装上让它能用起来？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777048405545,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cy6wkwx93o926bxyhdtstp"}}
