{"type":"message","id":"e76203b0","parentId":"8aba14c7","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:41:45.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The opencli bilibili hot command requires Browser Bridge extension. Let me try a command that doesn't need browser authentication.\n\nActually, let me try the Hacker News one since it's public.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHackerNews 热帖 TOP 10：\n\n| # | 标题 | 分数 | 评论 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | I Cancelled Claude: Token Issues, Declining Quality, and Poor Support | 71 | 18 |\n| 2 | Sabotaging projects by overthinking, scope creep, and structural diffing | 144 | 33 |\n| 3 | Norway Set to Become Latest Country to Ban Social Media for Under 16s | 159 | 111 |\n| 4 | Different Language Models Learn Similar Number Representations | 40 | 11 |\n| 5 | Spinel: Ruby AOT Native Compiler | 227 | 60 |\n| 6 | Why I'm Done Making Desktop Applications (2009) | 45 | 24 |\n| 7 | US special forces soldier arrested after allegedly winning $400k on Maduro raid | 521 | 557 |\n| 8 | Mounting tar archives as a filesystem in WebAssembly | 75 | 24 |\n| 9 | **DeepSeek v4** | **1526** | **1161** |\n| 10 | Show HN: How LLMs Work – Interactive visual guide | 219 | 53 |\n\nDeepSeek v4 的讨论量很猛啊，1500+ 分 1100+ 评论。\n\nB站的 `opencli` 命令目前跑不了，因为它需要 **Browser Bridge 扩展**（Chrome 插件）来复用你的登录态。装了这个扩展后，B站、小红书、Amazon 这些带 cookie 的网站就都能直接抓了。要不要我帮你装？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777048883577,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ffxno9r2xu6f70rmafsgw"}}
