{"type":"message","id":"df634912","parentId":"55eecd71","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:45:18.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 OpenCLI 的 Browser Bridge 扩展的问题。让我看看源码里有没有扩展，以及当前浏览器情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n源码里确实有扩展，在 `extension/` 目录下。但问题是：\n\n1. **需要先 build** — `extension/` 目录下的源码还没编译，得先 `npm run build`\n2. **你的浏览器是 Firefox** — Firefox 可以装 Chrome 扩展（通过 WebExtensions API 兼容），但需要手动加载\n\n不过有个更简单的方式——OpenCLI 有个 **standalone 模式**，不依赖浏览器扩展也能跑大部分公开 API 的命令。比如 HackerNews、arxiv、bbc 这些不需要 cookie 的，直接就能用。\n\n需要 cookie 的命令（B站热榜、小红书、Amazon）要装扩展的话，我可以帮你 build 然后装到 Firefox 里。要搞吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777049109002,"responseId":"chatcmpl-lj3kef9et4du2ltghwoioc"}}
