{"type":"message","id":"becc7f8b","parentId":"c3ad0d91","timestamp":"2026-04-24T16:48:20.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Firefox is installed. Let me check if we can load the extension programmatically or if we need to do it manually. Firefox on Linux doesn't have a simple CLI for installing extensions, so the user will need to do it manually.\n\nLet me just tell the user to load it manually since it's a one-time thing.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nFirefox 150 已经装好了。扩展 build 也完成了，但在 Linux 上 Firefox 没有 CLI 可以自动加载扩展，你需要手动操作一次：\n\n1. Firefox 地址栏输入 `about:debugging`\n2. 点 **\"This Firefox\"**\n3. 点 **\"临时加载附加组件\"**\n4. 选择 `/home/kensoulstar/OpenCLI-main/extension/manifest.json`\n\n加载成功后，B站、小红书、Amazon 那些需要 cookie 的命令就能跑了。要不要我帮你验证一下？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777049291116,"responseId":"chatcmpl-rp2jbi7sndkod6jdghs4y"}}
