{"type":"message","id":"80463ada","parentId":"8985e2c3","timestamp":"2026-04-24T17:10:25.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is having trouble selecting the directory in Firefox's file picker. The issue is that the file picker keeps trying to open subdirectories instead of accepting the parent directory. This is a common issue with Firefox's file picker when the directory has certain permissions or content.\n\nLet me think about possible solutions:\n\n1. The file picker might be having trouble because of how the directory is structured\n2. Maybe we can try selecting a parent directory and navigating up\n3. Or we could try a different approach\n\nActually, the issue is likely that Firefox's \"temporary extension\" picker wants to see the manifest.json file. The user should be able to select the directory itself, but if Firefox keeps trying to go into subdirectories, it might be a UI issue.\n\nThe fix is usually: in the file picker dialog, the user needs to select the **extension directory itself** (the folder containing manifest.json), not navigate into it. If Firefox keeps opening subdirectories, they should try selecting the parent directory name in the file list, not clicking on the folder icon.\n\n\nThe real issue might be that the file picker is treating the folder as a file to open rather than a directory to select—this can happen depending on the file manager behavior. I should guide them to use the keyboard shortcut or explicitly choose the parent directory instead of clicking into it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n不需要删子目录。问题是 Firefox 的文件选择器把目录当文件处理了。\n\n试试这个方法：\n\n1. 在文件选择器中，点 **\"上一步\"** 回到上一级目录（比如回到 `OpenCLI-main`）\n2. 然后在文件列表里**直接点击 `extension` 文件夹本身**（不要双击进去）\n3. 如果还是不行，试试按 **`Ctrl+L`** 调出地址栏，直接粘贴 `/home/kensoulstar/OpenCLI-main/extension/`，然后回车\n\n或者更简单的方式——**选择上一级目录 `OpenCLI-main`**，文件选择器应该会自动找到里面的 manifest.json。如果不行，你就在文件列表里找到 `manifest.json` 文件，直接选中它，Firefox 应该能自动识别它所在的目录。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777050604737,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9wby938pr4633d3o4zkzz8"}}
