{"type":"message","id":"85726f61","parentId":"e7457569","timestamp":"2026-04-24T17:25:38.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Chromium is running and the daemon is listening on port 19825. The extension is installed in Chromium but the connection isn't being established. This could be a snap sandbox issue - the snap version of Chromium might have restricted access to the extension or the local daemon.\n\nLet me check if the extension is properly loaded in Chromium and if there's a connectivity issue due to the snap sandbox.\n\nThe issue is likely that the snap version of Chromium has restricted filesystem access, which prevents the extension from connecting to the local daemon on port 19825.\n\nLet me try restarting the daemon and checking if there's a way to fix this.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nChromium 在跑，daemon 也在 19825 端口监听，但扩展连不上。这很可能是 **Chromium snap 沙箱** 限制了扩展访问本地端口的权限。\n\n你帮我确认一下：\n\n1. 在 Chromium 地址栏输入 `chrome://extensions`\n2. 找到 OpenCLI 扩展，确认状态是 **\"已启用\"**\n3. 点扩展的 **详情** 页面，看看有没有报错信息\n4. 也点一下扩展的 **选项/设置** 页面，确认它连接的是 `localhost:19825`\n\n另外，snap 版 Chromium 的扩展权限比较严，如果确认扩展已启用但还是连不上，可能需要给 snap 加权限：\n\n```bash\nsudo snap connect chromium:network-bind\n```\n\n你先看看扩展状态，我这边再排查。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777051508620,"responseId":"chatcmpl-h8fqptpqo9ra1fy6x43p44"}}
