{"type":"message","id":"7ce7ade3","parentId":"49908e52","timestamp":"2026-04-24T17:33:31.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是连不上。让我检查一下是不是 Chromium snap 的沙箱问题，或者扩展本身需要重新 build。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n还是没连上。让我看看是不是需要重新 build 扩展，或者 snap 沙箱的问题：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"447010831","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 snap 沙箱限制\nsnap connections chromium | grep -E 'network|loop' 2>/dev/null; echo \"---\"; snap interface network-bind 2>/dev/null; echo \"---\"; # 检查是否有 chromium 的 debugger 端口限制\ncat /home/kensoulstar/.config/opencli/daemon.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"no daemon config\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777052000045,"responseId":"chatcmpl-nhi8mmn30kqluv917w51kl"}}
