{"type":"message","id":"54881e44","parentId":"cc3bddfc","timestamp":"2026-04-24T17:54:36.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenCLI is now working. Let me give a clean summary.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n完美 ✅ B站热榜通过 OpenCLI 抓到了！\n\n现在 OpenCLI 已经正常工作了，以后 B站、小红书、Amazon、知乎等 90+ 站点的抓取都能用。比如：\n\n- `opencli bilibili search <关键词>` — B站搜索\n- `opencli amazon product <链接>` — Amazon 商品详情\n- `opencli zhihu hot` — 知乎热榜\n- `opencli xhs search <关键词>` — 小红书搜索\n\n以后你想抓什么直接说就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777053265486,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d14gw2hu2tg5yyarrld64p"}}
