{"type":"message","id":"0df82aae","parentId":"d72d9198","timestamp":"2026-04-24T17:55:25.534Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-25 01:55 GMT+8] 那我现在是不是要把这些网站用我的用户登录呢？"}],"timestamp":1777053325527}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb29a013","parentId":"0df82aae","timestamp":"2026-04-24T17:55:44.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问要不要登录网站，这涉及到 cookie 和认证的问题。让我看看 opencli 里哪些命令需要 cookie。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，大部分命令需要 cookie 才能拿到完整数据。\n\nopencli 里每个命令都标注了策略：\n- **public** — 不需要登录，直接抓\n- **cookie** — 需要登录态，会复用你 Chrome 里的 cookie\n- **intercept** — 需要浏览器拦截\n- **ui** — 需要控制桌面应用\n\n比如 B站热榜刚才能用是因为走的是公开 API，但像 B站关注列表、收藏夹、观看历史这些就需要登录。\n\n登录方式很简单——opencli 直接复用你 Chrome 的 cookie，你只要在 Chrome 里登录了对应网站就行。比如：\n\n- Chrome 登录了 B站 → `opencli bilibili history` 就能抓你的观看历史\n- Chrome 登录了 Amazon → `opencli amazon product <链接>` 能看到你的价格\n- Chrome 登录了小红书 → `opencli xhs search <关键词>` 能拿到个人化数据\n\n所以**你只需要在 Chrome 里登录你常用的网站**，opencli 就能自动复用 cookie，不需要额外配置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777053325541,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9aqoji9f0eaudfj1ryjw4g"}}
