{"type":"message","id":"7effa21a","parentId":"a95880e1","timestamp":"2026-04-24T19:03:21.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the best search strategy given the tools available. Let me think about what's available:\n\n1. **multi-search-engine** - OpenClaw skill for multi-engine search\n2. **opencli** - 90+ site CLI tools (HackerNews, arxiv, bbc, etc.)\n3. **web_fetch** - Direct URL fetching\n4. **browser** - Browser automation\n5. **OpenCLI browser commands** - Site-specific CLI commands\n\nLet me think about what the best approach is for different scenarios.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n目前搜索相关的工具有：\n\n**1. multi-search-engine 技能** — 多搜索引擎搜索，适合通用搜索\n**2. opencli** — 90+ 站点的专属 CLI，适合特定网站的数据抓取\n**3. web_fetch** — 直接抓取页面内容\n**4. browser** — 浏览器自动化，处理复杂交互\n\n---\n\n**最佳方案：分层使用**\n\n| 场景 | 用什么 | 为什么 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 找信息、查资料 | **multi-search-engine** | 一次搜多个引擎，覆盖面广 |\n| 查特定网站数据 | **opencli** | 结构化数据，稳定可靠 |\n| 找公开页面内容 | **web_fetch** | 轻量快速 |\n| 需要登录/JS 渲染 | **browser** | 万能兜底 |\n\n**实际工作流建议：**\n\n1. 先问 `multi-search-engine` 搜一圈，拿到结果概览\n2. 对感兴趣的结果，用 `opencli` 抓结构化数据（比如 `opencli amazon product <链接>`、`opencli bilibili search <关键词>`）\n3. 如果 opencli 没有对应站点，用 `web_fetch` 直接抓\n4. 需要登录或复杂交互的，用 `browser`\n\n**一句话总结：** 能用 opencli 就不用 web_fetch，能 web_fetch 就不用 browser。越结构化、越轻量越好。\n\n你具体想搜什么？我直接帮你跑。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777057376729,"responseId":"chatcmpl-i8a6eyakbaarvsiyr9foy"}}
